lines.text: Just what I needed, another bad habit!
I smell a baby... smells a lot like a baby named Johnny!
Don't get any blood on the baby!
Must have taken a great many blacksmiths to build that I imagine.
[shelley opens her apartment door in order to escape Rumpelstiltskin only to find him standing out side of it]
I've come to claim my prize! EEE.

[after he removes a broom handle that Shelley rammed down his throat]
Thy future is harsh on thy throat.

[to a motorcyclist]
I want your steed.
I only want the baby, John.

[riding on a motorcycle and wearing sun glasses]
Uncle Rumples' comin'!
Can I keep it? Can I take it home?
Sure. It's really interesting. You can take it home.
